>\n中國大飛機事業萬里長征走了又一步，我們一定要有自己的大飛機。<br />\n<br />\n當然，沒有人民支持，這些工作是難以做好的，我要為我們偉大的人民點讚。<br />\n<br />\n三隻手合力。<br />\n<br />\n輕關易道，通商寬衣。</blockquote><br />\n打飛機事業<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8dfe2b1b1467670abd02d65eb3d35a04fd81294","tid":446131,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T03:42:30.000Z","msg":"個名又長 16個字 <br />\n個內容又一鳩鳩 好像咩都有 又好像咩都無<br />\n<br />\n又話佢個咩文膽 王滬寧 三代帝師 好撚勁<br />\n<br />\n命衰過咩小學雞 改的火龍王 魂超剎 呢d<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbfeddba0e3748f17aa51cc5df039406f1dc0c5b","tid":446131,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T03:43:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個名又長 16個字 <br />\n個內容又一鳩鳩 好像咩都有 又好像咩都無<br />\n<br />\n又話佢個咩文膽 王滬寧 三代帝師 好撚勁<br />\n<br />\n命衰過咩小學雞 改的火龍王 魂超剎 呢d<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n中共中文不男係要幾空泛有幾空泛，咁到時要搬出嚟用果時就可以無限spin<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5280d87bd99c4ac58e375bf3f924deb78e98ca7","tid":446131,"uid":61300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T03:46:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Xi's think<br />\n<br />\n中文譯：屎的思想</blockquote><br />\nHoly Xi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d65128e18fb1ac64272829194b1f52cb572240fd","tid":446131,"uid":13468,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T03:50:50.000Z","msg":"雖然不明白是甚麼  但好像很厲害的樣子"},{"pid":"6a98c2974e8b70e9283f2344d0a1dda703a4ad1c","tid":446131,"uid":41821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T03:55:25.000Z","msg":"遲d支共d官員要見雜大帝要行三跪九叩之禮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔做即拉去勞改<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6853ef5ad8c546471bbf01747a961be251d94abd","tid":446131,"uid":30335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r